安装staf

【准备】
tar包 STAF3424-linux-ppc64le.tar

【安装】
1、解压STAF3424-linux-ppc64le.tar，解压后为staf目录
2、执行staf/STAFInst，默认安装到/usr/local/staf下
3、设置环境变量到/etc/profile
export PATH="/usr/local/staf/bin:${PATH}"
export STAFCONVDIR=/usr/local/staf/codepage
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="/usr/local/staf/lib:${LD_LIBRARY_PATH}"
export CLASSPATH="/usr/local/staf/lib/JSTAF.jar:${CLASSPATH}"
export CLASSPATH="/usr/local/staf/samples/demo/STAFDemo.jar:${CLASSPATH}"
4、配置/usr/local/staf/bin/STAF.cfg 
TRUST LEVEL 5 MACHINE 192.168.20.*
TRUST LEVEL 5 MACHINE 192.168.30.*
TRUST LEVEL 5 MACHINE 192.168.28.*
5、配置/etc/hosts
配置本机ip与主机名的映射
6、启动staf进程
/usr/local/staf/startSTAFProc.sh 
7、查看日志：当前目录下的nohup.out